		<title>Immunotherapy boosts chemotherapy in combating stage 3 colon cancer</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/immunotherapy-boosts-chemotherapy-in-combating-stage-3-colon-cancer/</link>
		
